<div class="container px-lg-5 main">
  <div class="mgin">
    <h1 class="fs-3 fw-bold mgin">Welcome to TopPop!</h1>
    <div class="fs-5 fw-bold mgin">How to play?</div>
    <p>You will be given 5 Top Pop music videos in random order. You need to sort them from most views to least views. Let's play!</p>        
    <div class="fs-5 fw-bold mgin">Enter your username</div>
    <p>Username should only contains letters, numbers and underscore. For example, you can be "pro_1337" :))</p>
  </div>
  <form action="/player" id="player-name-form" method="POST" role="form">
    <div class="row vertical-align query-bar">
      <div class="col-md-10 col-sm-3">
        <input class="form-control" id="player-name" name="player_name" type="text" required/>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-3">
        <button class="submit btn btn-lg btn-primary" id="player-name-submit" type="submit" value="submit">Play</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </form>
</div>